  <zone type="main">
    <line>love and humanity but am I not alone</line>
    <line>miserably alone – <delSpan spanTo="#c56-0127.01"/>None to love me but</line>
    <line>all fly and<anchor xml:id="c56-0127.01"/> You, my creator abhor me</line>
    <line>What hope <mod type="subst"><del rend="strikethrough">have I then from your</del><add
          resp="#pbs" place="superlinear">can I gather from</add></mod></line>
    <line>fellow creatures <mod type="additions" resp="#pbs"><add place="sublinear"
          >&#x2038;</add><add place="superlinear">who owe me nothing.</add></mod>—They spurn and
        <mod type="subst"><del rend="strikethrough">abhor</del><add resp="#pbs" place="sublinear"
          >&#x2038;</add><add resp="#pbs" place="superlinear">hate</add></mod></line>
    <line>me. The desart mountains and mourful</line>
    <line>glaciers are my refuge—I have wandered</line>
    <line>here many days– The caves of ice <mod type="subst"><del rend="strikethrough">are
          my</del><add place="superlinear">which <unclear unit="chars" extent="1" precision="low"
            reason="illegible"><metamark/></unclear></add></mod></line>
    <line>I only do not fear are a dwelling to me and</line>
    <line>the only one which man does not grudge</line>
    <line><mod type="deletions"><del rend="strikethrough">to me</del> – <del rend="strikethrough"
          >And food </del></mod>— These bleak skies I </line>
    <line>hail for they are kinder <add place="superlinear">to me</add> than <mod type="subst"
        xml:id="c56-0127.02" next="#c56-0127.03"><del rend="strikethrough">man</del><add
          place="superlinear">your fellow <mod type="subst"><del>creatures</del><add
              place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add><add place="superlinear">beings</add><add><ptr
                target="#c56-0127.04"/></add></mod></add></mod></line>
    <line><mod type="deletions" xml:id="c56-0127.03" prev="#c56-0127.02" next="#c56-0127.05"><del
          rend="triple-strike">and</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough">But I no</del><del rend="strikethrough"><add place="sublinear"
            >&#x2038;</add><add place="superlinear">Man</add></del>
        <del rend="strikethrough">They</del>
        <del rend="strikethrough">hates me and if</del></mod></line>
    <line><mod type="subst" prev="#c56-0127.03" xml:id="c56-0127.05"><del rend="strikethrough"
          >they</del><del rend="strikethrough"><add place="superlinear">he</add></del></mod> knew of
      my existence <mod type="additions"><add place="sublinear" resp="#pbs">&#x2038;</add><add
          place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">they</add> would <add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add><add
          place="superlinear">do</add></mod> as you</line>
    <line>arm themselves for my destruction – <del rend="strikethrough">And</del></line>
    <line>Shall I not <add place="superlinear">then</add> hate them who abhor me</line> my <line>I
        <mod type="additions"><add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add><add place="superlinear"
          >will</add></mod> keep no <del rend="strikethrough">temm</del> terms with <mod
        type="additions"><add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add><add place="superlinear"
        >my</add></mod> enemies <del rend="strikethrough">and</del></line>
    <line>I am miserable &amp; they shall share my</line>
    <line>wretchedness– Yet it is in your power</line>
    <line>to recompense me and deliver them from</line>
    <line>an evil which <mod type="subst"><del rend="strikethrough">you</del><add resp="#pbs"
          place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add><add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">it</add><add><ptr
            target="#c56-0127.06"/></add></mod>
      <del rend="strikethrough">have bestowed on them</del>.</line>
    <line>Let your compassion and justice be</line>
    <line>moved and do not disdain me. Listen</line>
    <line>to my tale ! when you have heard that</line>
    <line>deny or comiserate<del rend="cross-hatch">d</del> me as you shall</line>
    <line>judge <add place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">that</add> I deserve. But <mod type="subst"
          ><del rend="strikethrough">here</del><add place="sublinear">&#x2038;</add><add
          place="superlinear">hear</add></mod> me –The</line>
    <line>guilty <del rend="strikethrough">may</del> are allowed by human laws,</line>
    <line>bloody as they <mod type="subst"><del rend="strikethrough">are</del><add
          place="superlinear" resp="#pbs">may be</add></mod>, to speak in their <add resp="#pbs"
        place="superlinear">own</add> defence</line>
    <line><add resp="#pbs" place="superlinear">before they are condemned</add> Listen to me
      Frankenstein <del rend="strikethrough">for you are</del></line>
